WEBVTT

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:02.149
Hey, good morning family. How are y'all

00:00:02.159 --> 00:00:04.309
doing? It's evening here now, but I

00:00:04.319 --> 00:00:05.590
always say good morning because it's

00:00:05.600 --> 00:00:09.589
morning somewhere. I always

00:00:09.599 --> 00:00:12.150
come here to this campus because of

00:00:12.160 --> 00:00:13.749
what the Lord has showed me

00:00:13.749 --> 00:00:13.759
is

00:00:13.759 --> 00:00:16.150
coming here. And these praying hands

00:00:16.160 --> 00:00:18.710
when I drive by, they mean so

00:00:18.720 --> 00:00:21.510
much to me. You know, the motto of

00:00:21.520 --> 00:00:24.070
the school is 'Make no little plans

00:00:24.070 --> 00:00:24.080
here.'This

00:00:24.080 --> 00:00:26.790
is the ORU campus, by the

00:00:26.800 --> 00:00:29.589
way. I was driving by

00:00:29.599 --> 00:00:31.269
tonight and the Holy

00:00:31.279 --> 00:00:33.670
Spirit was just stirring in me so strong

00:00:33.680 --> 00:00:36.150
about the revival that's about to take

00:00:36.160 --> 00:00:38.549
place at this campus. You know, it's

00:00:38.559 --> 00:00:41.430
just what faith will build, what faith

00:00:41.440 --> 00:00:43.430
will do when you use your

00:00:43.440 --> 00:00:45.830
faith like a muscle.

00:00:45.840 --> 00:00:48.709
It's important, y'all.

00:00:48.719 --> 00:00:51.430
I drive by this because it

00:00:51.440 --> 00:00:54.310
inspires me to think big. It inspires me

00:00:54.320 --> 00:00:55.830
because this is what Oral Roberts

00:00:55.840 --> 00:00:58.709
believed God for. Every

00:00:58.719 --> 00:01:00.470
day I try to drive around here at

00:01:00.480 --> 00:01:02.709
least once and try to come over here and

00:01:02.719 --> 00:01:04.950
just inspire myself. The towers

00:01:04.960 --> 00:01:06.710
over there where the hospital

00:01:06.710 --> 00:01:06.720
was—I

00:01:06.720 --> 00:01:08.469
know they've sold that recently, I

00:01:08.479 --> 00:01:11.270
believe—but

00:01:11.280 --> 00:01:13.510
just the center, because the Lord

00:01:13.520 --> 00:01:15.510
showed me there will be a major

00:01:15.520 --> 00:01:18.070
outpouring of the spirit of the Lord in

00:01:18.080 --> 00:01:20.950
that big coliseum once again. The old

00:01:20.960 --> 00:01:23.910
wells of revival are coming uncapped.

00:01:23.920 --> 00:01:25.510
He told me, and I come over and

00:01:25.520 --> 00:01:27.190
I look at the prayer tower.

00:01:27.200 --> 00:01:29.429
Can you see the prayer tower over there?

00:01:29.439 --> 00:01:31.429
The prayer tower right there—it's right

00:01:31.439 --> 00:01:34.069
over there. That's where they pray.

00:01:34.079 --> 00:01:37.429
And I just thought, you know,

00:01:37.439 --> 00:01:38.870
it's exciting because some of the

00:01:38.880 --> 00:01:41.190
greatest ministers of

00:01:41.200 --> 00:01:43.910
any generation—I mean, I believe

00:01:43.920 --> 00:01:47.270
from Kathryn Kuhlman to Benny Hinn to all

00:01:47.280 --> 00:01:49.109
the greats that have come

00:01:49.119 --> 00:01:51.350
through here and had healing

00:01:51.360 --> 00:01:54.230
services and deliverance services where,

00:01:54.240 --> 00:01:56.069
you know, their ministry may not be all

00:01:56.079 --> 00:01:59.910
that it was back then, but look at what

00:01:59.920 --> 00:02:03.190
God did at one point in time through

00:02:03.200 --> 00:02:05.590
this right here. And what

00:02:05.600 --> 00:02:07.510
an amazing thing that he's doing and I

00:02:07.520 --> 00:02:08.949
know that he's going to do again. I

00:02:08.959 --> 00:02:10.710
showed you Victory and it's just right

00:02:10.720 --> 00:02:13.670
there. And I'm just excited because

00:02:13.680 --> 00:02:15.910
expectation brings

00:02:15.920 --> 00:02:17.990
manifestation. And it has nothing to

00:02:18.000 --> 00:02:19.670
even do with me. It's just something

00:02:19.680 --> 00:02:22.710
that I pray over because I know that God

00:02:22.720 --> 00:02:26.070
is going to visit the young generation,

00:02:26.080 --> 00:02:29.270
this young youth again with one last

00:02:29.280 --> 00:02:32.470
call, one last harvest, a major harvest

00:02:32.480 --> 00:02:35.110
of souls like we've never seen before

00:02:35.120 --> 00:02:37.589
and the glory of the Lord with fire. I

00:02:37.599 --> 00:02:39.110
believe that there'll be signs

00:02:39.120 --> 00:02:40.949
and wonders in the last days like it did

00:02:40.959 --> 00:02:43.030
with Azusa Street when there was a

00:02:43.040 --> 00:02:45.750
pillar of fire that was shown over

00:02:45.750 --> 00:02:45.760
Azusa

00:02:45.760 --> 00:02:47.270
Street. And I'm believing there'll be a

00:02:47.280 --> 00:02:49.910
pillar of fire over this Mabee Center and

00:02:49.920 --> 00:02:52.150
there'll be a pillar of fire over this

00:02:52.150 --> 00:02:52.160
ORU

00:02:52.160 --> 00:02:54.550
campus and that there will be a

00:02:54.560 --> 00:02:57.270
greater revival than even

00:02:57.280 --> 00:02:59.589
what happened at Asbury. You know that

00:02:59.599 --> 00:03:01.430
revival, I don't know, I guess it

00:03:01.440 --> 00:03:03.990
kind of fizzled out, but my goodness,

00:03:04.000 --> 00:03:05.750
I know that we're on the cusp of

00:03:05.760 --> 00:03:08.070
something huge about to take place in

00:03:08.080 --> 00:03:11.589
this Tulsa metroplex area and that

00:03:11.599 --> 00:03:13.350
God is about to do something huge in

00:03:13.360 --> 00:03:15.670
these last days. The Lord showed me

00:03:15.680 --> 00:03:18.470
Pastor Billy Joe Daugherty's son Paul Daugherty at

00:03:18.480 --> 00:03:19.990
that church right there, that there'll be

00:03:20.000 --> 00:03:23.110
an extension of the revival that's about

00:03:23.120 --> 00:03:25.830
to take place at ORU.

00:03:25.830 --> 00:03:25.840
And

00:03:25.840 --> 00:03:28.710
this is a massive church there,

00:03:28.720 --> 00:03:31.589
Victory. Well, Diana's with me now and

00:03:31.599 --> 00:03:33.830
it was so cold I had to get out

00:03:33.840 --> 00:03:36.070
of being outside. I told her, I

00:03:36.080 --> 00:03:38.149
said, 'I can't make this

00:03:38.149 --> 00:03:38.159
video.'I

00:03:38.159 --> 00:03:40.149
was trying to go and make the video at

00:03:40.159 --> 00:03:42.630
the campus and I was freezing. The wind

00:03:42.640 --> 00:03:44.949
was blowing so hard and it was cold

00:03:44.959 --> 00:03:47.430
and I told Braden, I said, 'Are

00:03:47.440 --> 00:03:48.630
you cold?'He goes, 'Yeah.'I said, 'I'm

00:03:48.640 --> 00:03:51.110
cold, too. Let's

00:03:51.110 --> 00:03:51.120
go.'So,

00:03:51.120 --> 00:03:54.550
you know, we have such an urgency

00:03:54.560 --> 00:03:57.350
though as we make the rest of this video

00:03:57.360 --> 00:03:59.429
for you all.

00:03:59.439 --> 00:04:01.509
The things the Lord has been putting on

00:04:01.519 --> 00:04:03.350
our hearts

00:04:03.360 --> 00:04:06.949
is he said, 'Brandon, people are not

00:04:06.959 --> 00:04:11.030
awake yet. There's no sense of urgency.

00:04:11.040 --> 00:04:13.589
Even in the upper leadership, they have

00:04:13.599 --> 00:04:17.110
a form of urgency, but deep down in

00:04:17.120 --> 00:04:20.150
their heart, there's not a

00:04:20.150 --> 00:04:20.160
stirring.'And

00:04:20.160 --> 00:04:21.189
people go, 'Well, you're judging

00:04:21.189 --> 00:04:21.199
people.'No,

00:04:21.199 --> 00:04:22.870
I'm not judging people. I'm

00:04:22.880 --> 00:04:25.749
just saying what he says. I have no idea

00:04:25.759 --> 00:04:28.310
what you feel, but I know what the Holy

00:04:28.320 --> 00:04:29.909
Spirit has told me, and I'm just going

00:04:29.919 --> 00:04:32.390
by what he said. So, if you don't agree

00:04:32.400 --> 00:04:34.629
with it, take it up with him. All I can

00:04:34.639 --> 00:04:36.710
say is what he's told me and what

00:04:36.720 --> 00:04:39.270
we pray about. And the Lord

00:04:39.280 --> 00:04:42.310
said, 'I'm going to bring a greater

00:04:42.320 --> 00:04:46.310
shaking to awaken beyond anybody's

00:04:46.320 --> 00:04:47.909
comprehension of what's about to happen,

00:04:47.919 --> 00:04:50.629
folks. I'm telling you, a major

00:04:50.629 --> 00:04:50.639
shaking.'And

00:04:50.639 --> 00:04:52.390
people go, 'Well,

00:04:52.400 --> 00:04:54.230
that sounds like

00:04:54.230 --> 00:04:54.240
fear.'You

00:04:54.240 --> 00:04:56.629
know, Diana and I are talking about a

00:04:56.639 --> 00:04:58.150
lot of the people that we've come in

00:04:58.160 --> 00:04:59.350
contact with. They say,

00:04:59.360 --> 00:05:01.189
'Well, you're a fearmonger or

00:05:01.189 --> 00:05:01.199
whatever.'They've

00:05:01.199 --> 00:05:02.790
said that before

00:05:02.800 --> 00:05:07.189
to us in the past and

00:05:07.199 --> 00:05:10.070
maybe, just maybe, your channel has

00:05:10.080 --> 00:05:11.909
grown so much because you preach a lot

00:05:11.919 --> 00:05:16.310
of fear because fear sells.

00:05:16.320 --> 00:05:19.110
But folks, it's not fear.

00:05:19.120 --> 00:05:22.150
It's an awakening unto God. And if

00:05:22.160 --> 00:05:24.870
you're in fear, it's

00:05:24.880 --> 00:05:27.350
because you're not awake.

00:05:27.360 --> 00:05:30.629
Your heart should be looking vertical

00:05:30.639 --> 00:05:32.710
with him. And that shouldn't scare you

00:05:32.720 --> 00:05:34.070
whenever he said these things are going

00:05:34.080 --> 00:05:36.629
to happen because why? We're dead to

00:05:36.639 --> 00:05:39.430
self. We are looking for the coming of

00:05:39.440 --> 00:05:41.350
the Lord Jesus Christ. And we have an

00:05:41.360 --> 00:05:43.430
urgency. And he told me, he said,

00:05:43.440 --> 00:05:46.150
'Brandon, there's no urgency. There's no

00:05:46.160 --> 00:05:48.950
urgency in my body. There's no urgency

00:05:48.960 --> 00:05:51.670
right now. Do you really realize I'm on

00:05:51.680 --> 00:05:54.230
my way? Do you really realize that this

00:05:54.240 --> 00:05:57.029
is the last call for the harvest of

00:05:57.039 --> 00:05:59.510
souls, the greatest harvest of souls

00:05:59.520 --> 00:06:02.469
this world has ever seen

00:06:02.469 --> 00:06:02.479
before?'As

00:06:02.479 --> 00:06:05.830
we sit on ORU campus with these

00:06:05.840 --> 00:06:08.070
hands, they mean something. They mean

00:06:08.080 --> 00:06:12.150
prayer changes things. They mean to me

00:06:12.160 --> 00:06:15.749
as I drive by it that somebody

00:06:15.759 --> 00:06:18.309
used their faith to get those hands

00:06:18.319 --> 00:06:19.830
there. That probably cost a lot of

00:06:19.840 --> 00:06:21.990
money. Behind us, that campus that you

00:06:22.000 --> 00:06:24.309
all seen, the Mabee Center, cost millions

00:06:24.319 --> 00:06:27.350
of dollars. It was Oral

00:06:27.350 --> 00:06:27.360
Roberts'faith

00:06:27.360 --> 00:06:29.830
that brought that forth using

00:06:29.840 --> 00:06:32.230
his faith like a

00:06:32.230 --> 00:06:32.240
tool—not

00:06:32.240 --> 00:06:35.110
a weapon, but a tool—a tool that he

00:06:35.120 --> 00:06:38.629
continually used to build his campus, to

00:06:38.639 --> 00:06:41.430
build the university for God.

00:06:41.440 --> 00:06:43.909
And he gave all the glory to God taking

00:06:43.919 --> 00:06:46.550
healing to the nations, raising up

00:06:46.560 --> 00:06:48.309
doctors, doing all the things that he did

00:06:48.319 --> 00:06:50.629
in his generation. But the Lord said,

00:06:50.639 --> 00:06:54.790
'Brandon, there's one more wave.

00:06:54.800 --> 00:06:57.909
There's one more wave of revival. Those

00:06:57.919 --> 00:07:01.350
old wells that had been

00:07:01.350 --> 00:07:01.360
capped,'the

00:07:01.360 --> 00:07:02.950
Lord said, 'I capped them.'He said,

00:07:02.960 --> 00:07:05.830
'I'm uncapping those wells.'And as you

00:07:05.840 --> 00:07:07.990
saw that church, Victory, he said,

00:07:08.000 --> 00:07:10.550
'Brandon, there, Victory and

00:07:10.550 --> 00:07:10.560
ORU

00:07:10.560 --> 00:07:12.070
will be an extension of each other in

00:07:12.080 --> 00:07:15.749
the days ahead, and you will see a major

00:07:15.759 --> 00:07:18.309
outpouring of the spirit of the Lord

00:07:18.319 --> 00:07:20.950
greater than even Asbury. That was

00:07:20.960 --> 00:07:23.430
nothing compared to what's about to

00:07:23.440 --> 00:07:25.990
happen with that Mabee Center. That's

00:07:26.000 --> 00:07:28.309
nothing compared to what we're about to

00:07:28.319 --> 00:07:31.270
see all throughout Tulsa

00:07:31.280 --> 00:07:33.350
with Victory Church. That Victory Church

00:07:33.360 --> 00:07:35.189
across the street—I don't know how many

00:07:35.199 --> 00:07:37.270
seats that holds, probably a

00:07:37.270 --> 00:07:37.280
10,000-seat

00:07:37.280 --> 00:07:39.110
auditorium. That's a massive one. And

00:07:39.120 --> 00:07:40.469
then they have the Mabee Center. And I don't

00:07:40.479 --> 00:07:42.469
know how many seats that holds. The

00:07:42.469 --> 00:07:42.479
Mabee

00:07:42.479 --> 00:07:44.950
Center is a little over 10,000 seats.

00:07:44.960 --> 00:07:46.629
Okay. So, you have 10,000 seats in the

00:07:46.629 --> 00:07:46.639
Mabee

00:07:46.639 --> 00:07:48.469
Center. Thanks, babe. Ten

00:07:48.469 --> 00:07:48.479
thousand

00:07:48.479 --> 00:07:50.309
seats in the Mabee Center. We

00:07:50.319 --> 00:07:51.749
have

00:07:52.080 --> 00:07:53.430
5,000 at Victory Church.

00:07:53.440 --> 00:07:57.270
Okay. So, 15,000 seat capacity

00:07:57.280 --> 00:07:58.869
between the two. That's amazing. And

00:07:58.879 --> 00:08:01.510
they could do simulcast, make it live,

00:08:01.520 --> 00:08:03.189
have an overflow, but it doesn't matter

00:08:03.199 --> 00:08:05.430
