00:08:05.440 --> 00:08:09.510
radical move of the spirit of God one

00:08:09.520 --> 00:08:11.909
last time.

00:08:11.919 --> 00:08:15.830
'One last call,'he said.

00:08:15.840 --> 00:08:17.830
And now I see it. Do you remember I told

00:08:17.840 --> 00:08:19.670
you he was going to use the angels? He

00:08:19.680 --> 00:08:21.270
told me, he said, 'Brandon, I'm sending

00:08:21.280 --> 00:08:23.110
my reserves,

00:08:23.120 --> 00:08:25.430
my angel army reserves. I'm sending

00:08:25.430 --> 00:08:25.440
them.'There's

00:08:25.440 --> 00:08:27.189
