00:09:06.080 --> 00:09:10.150
But he got radically on

00:09:10.160 --> 00:09:13.030
fire going to Azusa Street. There is a

00:09:13.040 --> 00:09:15.350
cross-pollination

00:09:15.360 --> 00:09:20.389
