00:09:20.399 --> 00:09:23.190
light somebody else on fire.

00:09:23.200 --> 00:09:26.470
It's not going to be just about the

00:09:26.480 --> 00:09:29.509
churches, folks. God told me

00:09:29.519 --> 00:09:31.269
