00:09:37.600 --> 00:09:39.670
forth with the young people

00:09:39.680 --> 00:09:41.910
there.

00:09:41.920 --> 00:09:43.670
So that's why I go and I pray and I

00:09:43.680 --> 00:09:45.910
drive around it. You go all

