down Lewis Avenue and I just circle

00:09:48.000 --> 00:09:50.070
around,

00:09:50.080 --> 00:09:52.230
just praying in the spirit, seeing the

00:09:52.240 --> 00:09:55.350
Lord show me something else. I'm hungry.

00:09:55.360 --> 00:09:57.110
I'm desperate.

00:09:57.120 --> 00:10:01.590
I want change. I am so tired of having

00:10:01.600 --> 00:10:04.710
church that's just normal.

00:10:04.720 --> 00:10:07.190
I know it's like, what are

00:10:07.200 --> 00:10:08.710
