00:10:38.880 --> 00:10:43.030
I've been there. I've seen it. I know

00:10:43.040 --> 00:10:45.350
exactly what the Lord is saying in my

00:10:45.360 --> 00:10:48.230
heart. He's shaking me to awaken me

