00:11:00.399 --> 00:11:02.470
a storm coming. I'm here to tell you all

00:11:02.480 --> 00:11:04.550
there's a heaven to gain and a hell to

00:11:04.560 --> 00:11:08.630
shun. I'm trying to wake you up to tell

00:11:08.640 --> 00:11:11.030
you all with urgency, to shake you

00:11:11.030 --> 00:11:11.040
until

00:11:11.040 --> 00:11:13.269
your teeth rattle, to tell

00:11:13.279 --> 00:11:15.110
you, "Listen

00:11:15.120 --> 00:11:18.230
to me, Jesus is

00:11:18.240 --> 00:11:20.710
coming."When

00:11:20.720 --> 00:11:23.190
I went through tribulation with him and

00:11:23.200 --> 00:11:24.870
he took me out of my body—I don't know

00:11:24.880 --> 00:11:26.550
if I was in my body or out of my

00:11:26.550 --> 00:11:26.560
body—I

00:11:26.560 --> 00:11:28.150
don't know what happened. All I

00:11:28.160 --> 00:11:30.470
know is I was there,

